7253629","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a971e216f064fe1068249f79038e9a652b1243","tid":1708124,"uid":116775,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"學生要停課！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707305</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(理性討論)教育局死唔叫停中小學，係陰謀！<br />\n<br />\n因為停左中小學會間接造就大罷工，此仍大大粒春袋！試討論如何達致中小學合理地停課或被停課～<br />\n<br />\n[UPDATED]<br />\n港大、浸大、中大、理大、科大、恒大、教大、公大、職訓局、Ive及演藝學院<br />\n宣布明日停課<br />\n--- --- --- ---<br />\n教育局肯停課未？<br />\n有冇人一齊draft 封中文信俾家長，<br />\n一人一信sd 去中小學要求停課！<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少babykingdom c9 家長既力量<br />\n罷工罷學<br />\n俾國際見到！<br />\n--- --- --- --- ---<br />\n《要求學校停課template》<br />\nTo: EDB &amp; 教協<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-mQuVXzgpZxlXS57MYfHtcyU0CfwN4bf1YwOahX7v0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-mQuVXzgpZxlXS57MYfHtcyU0CfwN4bf1YwOahX7v0U&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=d020588f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-mQuVXzgpZxlXS57MYfHtcyU0CfwN4bf1YwOahX7v0U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uPwvODfLS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uPwvODfLS&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=c79e8637\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uPwvODfLS&h=2bd38de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uPwvODfLS</a><br />\n更多原因:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uErEzDnuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uErEzDnuA&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=9bce8d01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uErEzDnuA&h=72b848aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uErEzDnuA</a><br />\n<br />\n如遇意外，敢問學校的第三者保險是否涵蓋，以及校方能否承擔學生人命傷亡的責任？<br />\n<br />\n基於保障學生安全，作為貴校學校的家長，督請 貴校考慮自行安排停課。期望 貴校盡早作出決定，讓家長有足夠時間安排人手照顧子女。"},{"pid":"339ca0b3036418209f9b3e843a8c5854961432ba","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾教育局"},{"pid":"388c51192303609d66a6280ae5692609806799c3","tid":1708124,"uid":127791,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"幼稚園小學咁大個人識自己照顧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點可以小小事就唔返學"},{"pid":"a43787d66aaf791bf83b3584213f2dd3900c2896","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85d1ab77e5f9bc7c6e46501c5528756de2ac01b0","tid":1708124,"uid":49853,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"政府logic:停課=跪低"},{"pid":"f985e88301a463d4afed86875379f54256d590bb","tid":1708124,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6ffdec0dfe7af951bddedec71063867430be4b1","tid":1708124,"uid":65911,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"因為小學幼稚園一停 班家長就返唔到工返屋企湊仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23168022424497482e20866d0966348c124db57c","tid":1708124,"uid":330298,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"Cls 中小學對催淚彈免疫？"},{"pid":"53fc5845b1ff955cf05485a3aa49cdf174063775","tid":1708124,"uid":151544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"388c51192303609d66a6280ae5692609806799c3","tid":1708124,"uid":127791,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"幼稚園小學咁大個人識自己照顧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/p