o-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6dec8c6c4ad07ba8fc315c2568a5b16cf9ac9b63","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d2bc4d64d77b76a5f7915b119a939a00a3a9af","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a971e216f064fe1068249f79038e9a652b1243","tid":1708124,"uid":116775,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"學生要停課！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707305</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(理性討論)教育局死唔叫停中小學，係陰謀！<br />\n<br />\n因為停左中小學會間接造就大罷工，此仍大大粒春袋！試討論如何達致中小學合理地停課或被停課～<br />\n<br />\n[UPDATED]<br />\n港大、浸大、中大、理大、科大、恒大、教大、公大、職訓局、Ive及演藝學院<br />\n宣布明日停課<br />\n--- --- --- ---<br />\n教育局肯停課未？<br />\n有冇人一齊draft 封中文信俾家長，<br />\n一人一信sd 去中小學要求停課！<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少babykingdom c9 家長既力量<br />\n罷工罷學<br />\n俾國際見到！<br />\n--- --- --- --- ---<br />\n《要求學校停課template》<br />\nTo: EDB &amp; 教協<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-mQuVXzgpZxlXS57MYfHtcyU0CfwN4bf1YwOahX7v0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-mQuVXzgpZxlXS57MYfHtcyU0CfwN4bf1YwOahX7v0U&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=d020588f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-mQuVXzgpZxlXS57MYfHtcyU0CfwN4bf1YwOahX7v0U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uPwvODfLS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uPwvODfLS&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=c79e8637\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uPwvODfLS&h=2bd38de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uPwvODfLS</a><br />\n更多原因:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uErEzDnuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uErEzDnuA&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=9bce8d01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uErEzDnuA&h=72b848aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uErEzDnuA</a><br />\n<br />\n如遇意外，敢問學校的第三者保險是否涵蓋，以及校方能否承擔學生人命傷亡的責任？<br />\n<br />\n基於保障學生安全，作為貴校學校的家長，督請 貴校考慮自行安排停課。期望 貴校盡早作出決定，讓家長有足夠時間安排人手照顧子女。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733bfee0703050a5236632e50b08368c091b8f15","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ab86557442a0a2e1686cbee441e970ebbc04ec","tid":1708124,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n講返先 已經有中學聽日停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0535655e54cf50ac5ee0c75ab2c049de27890e","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T22:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d687d24d9591b8299cf1c018d1a29235e583b9c","tid":1708124,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T22:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52ef7f3444f7896cea091ee301da180bb9c93c7","tid":1708124,"uid":186